---
import { Comment } from 'astro-pure/advanced'
import { Timeline } from 'astro-pure/user'
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/CommonPage.astro'
import AccountCard from '@/components/about/AccountCard.astro'
import ToolSection from '@/components/about/ToolSection.astro'

const headings = [
  { depth: 2, slug: 'hobbies', text: 'Hobbies' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'lang', text: 'Programming Languages' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'tools', text: 'Tools' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'peronal', text: 'Personal Info' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'about-blog', text: 'About Blog' }
]
---

<PageLayout title='About' {headings} info='/about'>
  {/* Quotation */}
  <blockquote class='my-6 border-l-4 border-primary pl-4 italic text-muted-foreground'>
    <p>My world is what I make of it.</p>
    <footer class='mt-2 text-sm mb-2' style='justify-self:end'>
      â€” <i>I Am</i>, a film from World Creator
    </footer>
  </blockquote>

  <h3 class='mb-4 text-lg font-semibold'>TL;DR</h3>
  <p class='mb-8'>
    My name is Ray Zhang, but just call me Norb. I am a professional developer, amateur digital
    artist and indie game developer.
  </p>
  {/* general-talk */}
  <h2 id='hobbies'>All Walks of My Life</h2>
  <div>
    <p>
      I have a wide variety of hobbies, and have established myself in numerous communities, under
      different names. Here is a selected list of them:
    </p>
    <AccountCard
      class='mb-4'
      icon={import('/src/assets/logos/norb-logo-black-monotone.svg')}
      title='Home Page'
      subtitle='Under the name Norb'
      description='Where I host dev-related and personal blogs, along with other online services.'
      href='https://norb.space'
    />
    <AccountCard
      class='mb-4'
      icon={import('/src/assets/logos/github.svg')}
      title='GitHub'
      subtitle='Under the name RayZh-hs'
      description='Where I am an active developer of multiple open-source projects.'
      href='https://github.com/RayZh-hs'
    />
    <AccountCard
      class='mb-4'
      icon={import('/src/assets/logos/sketchfab.svg')}
      title='Sketchfab'
      subtitle='Under the name RayZh'
      description='Where I am a renowned content creator, using photogrammetry to capture life as it is.'
      href='https://sketchfab.com/horizon_studios'
    />
    <AccountCard
      class='mb-4'
      icon={import('/src/assets/logos/pexels.svg')}
      title='Pexels'
      subtitle='Under the name Ray Zhang'
      description='Where I showcase my works of photography.'
      href='https://www.pexels.com/@ray-zhang-2155334924/gallery/'
    />
  </div>

  {/* languages */}
  <h2 id='lang'>Programming Languages</h2>
  <p>As a full-stack developer, I am proficient in an expanding array of programming languages:</p>
  <ToolSection
    class='mb-5'
    tools={[
      {
        name: 'C++',
        description: 'Kernel and Algorithm Development',
        href: 'https://isocpp.org/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/cpp.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Python',
        description: 'Scripting and Automation',
        href: 'https://www.python.org/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/python.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'JavaScript/TypeScript',
        description: 'Web Development',
        href: 'https://www.typescriptlang.org/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/typescript.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Go',
        description: 'Internet Services',
        href: 'https://golang.org/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/golang.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Kotlin',
        description: 'Software Development',
        href: 'https://kotlinlang.org/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/kotlin.svg?raw')
      }
    ]}
  />

  {/* tools */}
  <h2 id='tools'>Tools</h2>
  <p>
    Given the wide range of hobbies that I have, I use a variety of tools. Currently am gradually
    migrating to open-source projects.
  </p>
  <ToolSection
    class='mb-5'
    title='Design and Art'
    tools={[
      {
        name: 'Photoshop',
        description: 'Picture Editing',
        href: 'https://www.adobe.com/products/photoshop',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/photoshop.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'After Effects',
        description: 'Motion Graphics',
        href: 'https://www.adobe.com/products/aftereffects',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/aftereffects.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Premiere Pro',
        description: 'Video Editing',
        href: 'https://www.adobe.com/products/premiere',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/premiere.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Blender',
        description: '3D Modeling and Rendering',
        href: 'https://www.blender.org/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/blender.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        // Sadly I cannot use the official logo due to copyright issues
        // See https://quadspinner.com/About/Brand for details
        name: 'Quadspinner Gaea',
        description: 'Procedural Terrain Generation',
        href: 'https://www.gaea.com/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/gaea.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Realityscan',
        description: 'Photogrammetry',
        href: 'https://www.capturingreality.com/',
        icon: {
          light: import('@/assets/tools/realityscan-light.svg?raw'),
          dark: import('@/assets/tools/realityscan-dark.svg?raw')
        }
      },
      {
        name: 'GIMP',
        description: 'Picture Editing',
        href: 'https://www.gimp.org/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/gimp.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Graphite',
        description: 'Procedual Image Editing and Vector Art',
        href: 'https://graphite.rs/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/graphite.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Kdenlive',
        description: 'Video Editing',
        href: 'https://kdenlive.org/en/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/kdenlive.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Unreal Engine',
        description: 'Cinematics and Rendering',
        href: 'https://www.unrealengine.com/',
        icon: {
          light: import('@/assets/tools/unreal-light.svg?raw'),
          dark: import('@/assets/tools/unreal-dark.svg?raw')
        }
      }
    ]}
  />
  <ToolSection
    class='mb-5'
    title='Development'
    tools={[
      {
        name: 'VS Code',
        description: 'IDE',
        href: 'https://code.visualstudio.com/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/vscode.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Jetbrains IDEs',
        description: 'IDE',
        href: 'https://www.jetbrains.com/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/jetbrains.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Termius',
        description: 'Remote Development',
        href: 'https://www.termius.com/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/termius.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Helix',
        description: 'Terminal Text Editor',
        href: 'https://helix-editor.com/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/helix.svg?raw')
      }
    ]}
  />
  <ToolSection
    class='mb-5'
    title='Environment'
    tools={[
      {
        name: 'Ubuntu 24.04 LTS',
        description: 'Development Machine',
        href: 'https://ubuntu.com/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/ubuntu.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Windows 11',
        description: 'Personal Machine',
        href: 'https://news.microsoft.com/windows11-general-availability/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/windows11.svg?raw')
      }
    ]}
  />

  {/* gossips */}
  <h2 id='peronal'>Personal Info</h2>
  <p>
    I am a student at Shanghai Jiao Tong University, majoring in Computer Science. Computers have
    been my passion since I was young, and that passion has only grown stronger over the years.
  </p>
  <p>
    I am strong in organizing and engineering complex projects, so I have led many open-source
    projects over the years. I am also a quick learner, and I am always eager to learn new
    technologies and skills.
  </p>
  <p>
    I lead a rich personal life. I enjoy photography, digital art, hiking and traveling. I am a
    regular tennis player and volleyball player. Born a nature lover, I have gained much knowledge
    about plants through my excursions in the wild.
  </p>

  {/* about-blog */}
  <h2 id='about-blog'>About Blog</h2>
  <p>
    The website is generated from template
    <a href='https://github.com/cworld1/astro-theme-pure' target='_blank'>Astro Theme Pure</a>
    , and is re-developed by me and my friend <a href='https://theunknownth.ing' target='_blank'>TheUnknownThing</a>.
  </p>
  <Timeline
    events={[
      {
        date: '2025-04-10',
        content:
          'Repo created on <a href="https://github.com/RayZh-hs/norb.space"target="_blank">Github</a>. Started front page development.'
      },
      {
        date: '2025-08-30',
        content:
          'First blog created and deployed locally.'
      },
      {
        date: '2025-09-10',
        content: 'Added gallery support for Astro Theme Pure.'
      },
      {
        date: '2025-10-10',
        content:
          'First version of the website deployed at <a href="https://norb.space" target="_blank">norb.space</a>.'
      }
    ]}
  />
  <Comment slot='bottom' />
</PageLayout>
